-- News Corp.'s Shine Taps Zigler for U.S. Digital Efforts
-- B y   A n d y   F i x m e r
-- 2012-08-28T19:13:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-28/news-corp-s-shine-taps-zigler-for-u-s-digital-efforts.html
News Corp. (NWSA) ’s Shine TV production
unit named Vivi Zigler president of its digital operations in
the U.S.  Zigler, most recently president of NBC Universal Digital
Entertainment, was named president of Shine 360 & Digital, Shine
America, according to an e-mailed statement today. She will
report to Carl Fennessy, Shine America’s chief executive.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andy Fixmer in Los Angeles at 
